content.title: Increase Validator Active Set to 130
content.description: This proposal raises the validator limit for Luna Classic from 100 to 130, welcoming back validators from Luna v2 after the TFL and SEC settlement. Expanding the validator set strengthens our network's decentralization and benefits the LUNC community.
